complete._states: [A, B, C, D, E, F, S]

convert_to_DSL:
finite state automaton TestName {
	A final [S1] -- np1 --> B initial
	A -- np1 --> E final [SB]
	A -- p1, r2 --> A
	A -- p1, r2 --> D final [SB]
	B -- r1 --> A
	B -- r2 --> C final [S2]
	B -- r2 --> F final [SB]
	C -- np2 --> B
	C -- np2 --> E
	C -- p2 --> F
	C -- p2, r1 --> C
	D -- np1 --> E
	D -- p1, r2 --> D
	E -- r2 --> F
	F -- np2 --> E
	F -- p2 --> F
}
